products.body_html:
The Winco RC-P300 rice cooker can accommodate 30 rice cups of uncooked rice—unlike regular cups, industry-standard rice cups hold 6 ounces. Employees can measure ingredients with the included measuring cup or pour rice straight into the inner pot, which has measurement marks on the interior. This pot can then be dropped into the cooker so rice can soak in the water. After 30 minutes of soaking, employees can pull the lever down, and the cooking cycle will begin. products.title: Waring WFP16SCD Bowl Food Processor
products.body_html:
Waring WFP16SCD 1 Speed Batch/Bowl Food Processor w/ 4 qt Bowl, 120v

 

The Waring WFP16SCD food processor combines several pieces of equipment in one. With its 4-quart batch bowl, cooks can quickly blend and purée soups, sauces, and dressings. Thanks to a unique Liquilock seal system, the bowl will not leak even when it is operated at its full capacity. A continuous feed accessory with chute allows cooks to continuously slice, dice, and grate a number of products, including cheese, processing hundreds of pounds an hour. The powerful 2-horsepower motor, die-cast housing, and metal drive shaft allow the Waring WFP16SCD to hold up to heavy-duty demands in the commercial kitchen.

 

FEACTURES
